item.title: Red Apple
item.dc:creator: uy
item.description: Naturally sweet and delicious, our Plum Halves in Rice Syrup contains no added beet or cane sugar. Picked at the peak of ripeness and minimally processed, our organic fruits are perfect for baking and topping desserts with or delicious when eaten with ice cream or on its own. This autumnal, sticky fig and granola breakfast bowl is the perfect start to the day. Made with roasted figs warm from the oven, our creamy organic Kefir and a spoonful of our crunchy oat granola. A breakfast perfect for the week ahead.
